{
  "stem": "20088.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So we did listen, and they did tell-- because I think this is important-- that they did know that there were concentration camps in the east, even they mentioned Buchenwald and Auschwitz, where there were gas chambers and where people were gassed and cremated.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we did know this information.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they kept giving us hope.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They said, if you are in hiding, be careful.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Stay in hiding.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It won't be so long anymore.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We'll try our best to finish the war as soon as possible.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And you know-- so we had hope.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And of course, when the Africa war started and the Germans were starting to lose, it was very hopeful for us.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because we went in hiding in June '42.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we thought, by Christmas it will be the end.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Nobody really thought a minute that it would last that long.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "If we would have known we would have to stay in hiding for years, you know, I don't think we might have-- perhaps not have attempted it.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because it was really very difficult.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And as well, my father had jewelry, and-- because the-- with us, I don't think our-- Mrs.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Klompe, I don't think she asked a lot of money.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But of course, life is expensive.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And with food being rationed and everything, it-- it was still quite a bit to pay.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But the woman where my father and brother was in hiding, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] she was a single woman.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And she started to blackmail them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "She wanted more and more money from my father.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And my father said, well-- he did give it, of course.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But eventually, he said, well, we-- we haven't got unlimited money.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "My mother had to sell-- she gave it to Mr.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
